translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  10,26,"Kwabo benze okulungileyo iya kuba ngumvuzo ongowona mhle nangaphezulu. Akuyi kubakho bumnyama, naluthuli, nahlazo liya kugquma ubuso babo. Bona bangabahlali basePaladesi baya kuhlala apho ngonaphakade"
  10,27,"Ke bona abo basebenzele izenzo ezingcolileyo, imbuyekezo yesenzo esingcolileyo yinto ekwafana naso, nehlazo elonyelisayo eliya kugquma (ubuso) babo, Akukho mkhuseli baya kumfumana kuAllâh. Ubuso babo buya kugqunywa bube ngathi zizicuku ngezicuku eziphuma kwinzulu yobumnyama yobusuku, ngabahlali baseMlilweni, (ke abo) abaya kuhlala apho ngonaphakade"
  10,28,"Kananjalo ngeMini leyo Siya kubaqundanisa ndaweninye bonke, Siya kuthi kwabo bayamanisa amahlulelane kuThi: “Yimani njalo ezindaweni zenu! Nina ndawonye namahlulelane enu (enaniwanqula)”. Size Sibahlukanise, aze amahlulelane abo athi: “Yayingesithi aba nanibanqula"
  10,29,"Ke kaloku uAllâh UliNgqina ngokwaneleyo phakathi kwethu nani, lokuba inene thina asazi nto ngokunqulwa kwethu nini.”"
  10,30,"Apho! Umntu ngamnye uya kuyazi into awayisebenzelayo ngaphambili, kananjalo (bonke) baza kumiswa phambi koAllâh, OyiNkosi yabo yokwenene, oothixo babo bobuxoki abaziyilela bona baya kunyamalala bangabikho phambi kwabo"
  10,31,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Ngubani na oninika umfunzelo ovela esibhakabhakeni nasemhlabeni? Ingubani uMnini kuva nokubona? Kanti ngubani Oveza abafileyo kwabaphilileyo? Ize ibe ngubani uMlungelelanisi wemicimbi?” Baza kuthi: “NguAllâh.” Yithi: “Ke ngoku anisoyiki (ngokuba nitheni na) isohlwayo sika-Allâh?”"
  10,32,"Lowo nguAllâh, iNkosi yenu yenyaniso, ke ngoku emveni kwenyaniso ingaba yintoni enye ngaphandle kokulahleka? Yintoni kanye ebaphambukisileyo"
  10,33,Elo ke liLizwi leNkosi yakho eligwetyelwa ngakhona ngokuchasene nabo bangabagwiliki abangakholwayo